A. Admin Emails Page (6 tasks)

  - A1. Email log viewer — reference table of all 16 email events with live/stubbed/not-built status
  - A2. Branded email template system — rich Mailchimp-style HTML base template (dark theme, gold accents, logo, social footer, CTA buttons)
  - A3. Built 14 email templates in src/lib/email.js — welcome, booking confirmation, cancellation, class cancelled by admin, pack purchase, credits low warning, removed from class, admin direct email, class changed,       
  private class invitation, waitlist promotion, class reminder, credit expiry warning, admin cancelled booking
  - A4. Wired templates into trigger points — register route, cancel route, admin cancel class, stripe webhook, booking create (low credit check), admin roster remove, admin schedule notify
  - A5. Admin compose email — form on Emails page to send direct email to any member (member search, subject, body)
  - A6. Email overview tab showing all 16 events with triggers and template status

  B. Admin Settings (3 tasks)

  - B1. Studio Info tab — name, address, phone, email, website (read/write studio_settings)
  - B2. Booking Rules tab — default capacity, cancellation window hours, max advance booking days
  - B3. Reminders tab — toggle 24h/1h reminder switches

  C. Missing Pages (3 tasks)

  - C1. Privacy Policy page (/privacy) — 9-section PDPA-compliant policy
  - C2. Terms of Service page (/terms) — 12-section terms with cancellation policy, health waiver
  - C3. 404 page (not-found.js) — branded dark theme with navigation links

  D. Admin Activity Page Redesign (3 tasks)

  - D1. Richer event cards — color-coded by type (green=booking, red=cancellation, blue=signup, amber=admin)
  - D2. Expandable detail view — full context with credit info, timestamps, late cancel flags
  - D3. Better filtering and grouping — events grouped by date, type filter pills, CSV export built in

  E. Employee Role (1 task)

  - E1. New employee role — middleware + UI enforcement across 14 admin API routes, sidebar filtering, restricted from settings/packs/design, blocked from role changes and member deactivation

  F. Member Dashboard Gaps (4 tasks)

  - F1. Waitlist positions in dashboard — active waitlist entries with position badges and leave button
  - F2. Private class badge — distinct visual for private classes in My Bookings
  - F3. Fixed iCal download — changed from window.open() to fetch+blob pattern
  - F4. Hue effect on bookings — category color system (purple=recurring, amber=private, sky=regular)

  G. Buy Packs Page Redesign (1 task)

  - G1. Full redesign — pricing psychology (anchor pricing, per-class cost, savings %), "Most Popular"/"Best Value" auto-detection, tiered cards with feature checklists, gold checkmarks, staggered motion animations

  H. Gamification & Member Profiles (5 tasks)

  - H1. Weekly streak tracker — consecutive weeks with at least 1 class
  - H2. Total classes counter — lifetime attendance
  - H3. Achievement badges — 12 badges (milestones, streaks, variety, time-based)
  - H4. Profile gamification display — widget on dashboard showing stats
  - H5. Badge showcase — expandable visual badge grid

  I. Admin Dashboard Review (1 task)

  - I1. Enhanced dashboard — revenue card (month, ฿), week-over-week trend indicators, "Needs Attention" widget (full/low-booking classes), recent cancellations feed with late cancel badges

  J. Admin Design/CMS Page (1 task)

  - J1. New /admin/design page — 4 tabs (Hero & Branding, Social Links, Contact Info, Gallery), all stored in studio_settings, admin-only with middleware protection

  K. Business Logic (6 tasks)

  - K1. Completed /api/admin/schedule/notify — sends sendClassChanged emails to all booked members
  - K2. Class type deactivation safety — blocks if future active classes exist
  - K3. Instructor deactivation safety — blocks if future active classes assigned
  - K4. Pack deactivation safety — blocks if members have active credits
  - K5. Freeze member — replaces deactivate, preserves data, blocks login, cancels future bookings (returns credits), removes from waitlists, reversible via unfreeze button
  - K6. Login redirect fix — proper same-tab redirect, frozen account error message

